SUMMARY:Epic Reads YA Meet Up at Quail Ridge Books
DESCRIPTION:https://www.eventbrite.com/e/epic-reads-ya-meet-up-at-quail-r
 idge-books-tickets-65729979137\n\nSo many YA booksso little time.EpicRea
 dsinvites readers of all ages to join a round-table where youll get to s
 trike up conversation with authorsKendare Blake\, Sara Raasch\, Shelby M
 ahurin\, and Rena Barronwho will gab about their books and other fan fav
 orites. A purchase of any of the authors new books is required to partic
 ipate (and you can bring books from home!). Small author dish sesh + kil
 ler YA books = a booklovers dream\, courtesy ofEpicReads.\nAttendees wil
 l be seated in small groups and the authors will rotate among the groups
 \, speed-dating style.The meet-up sessions will be followed by signing l
 ines.\nFAQs\nDo I need to buy a book to attend the event?\nYes. Since th
 e authors are touring to promote their newest titles\, you need to buy o
 ne ticket (book included) to attend. If you want to buy all four titles 
 with one ticket\, get 20% off by selecting the 4 Book Bundle ticket.\nEa
 ch ticket grants you entrance to the meet up and a signing line ticket.\
 nThere will not be any free\, unreserved seats available.\nTicket Option
 s:\nFIVE DARK FATES TICKET / $25.99\nOne ticket to participate in the Ep
 ic Reads Meet Up with all four authors. Includes a copy of Five Dark Fat
 es and a signing line ticket. \nAbout the book: In the final book in the
 #1New York TimesbestsellingThree Dark Crowns series\, an all-out war is 
 brewingone that will pit sister against sister and dead against undead. 
 \nTHESE DIVIDED SHORES TICKET / $25.99\nOne ticket to participate in the
  Epic Reads Meet Up with all four authors. Includes a copy of These Divi
 ded Shores and a signing line ticket. \nAbout the book: A thrilling sequ
 el toThese Rebel Wavesfull of deadly magic\, double crosses\, and a revo
 lutionfrom Sara Raasch\, theNew York Timesbestselling author of the Snow
  Like Ashes series. Perfect for fans of Shannon Hale\, Leigh Bardugo\, a
 nd Marissa Meyer. \nSERPENT AND DOVE TICKET / $25.99\nOne ticket to part
 icipate in the Epic Reads Meet Up with all four authors. Includes a copy
  of Serpent and Dove and a signing line ticket.\nAbout the book: Bound a
 s one\, to love\, honor\, or burn. Book one of a stunning fantasy duolog
 y\, this tale of witchcraft and forbidden love is perfect for fans of Ke
 ndare Blake and Sara Holland. \nKINGDOM OF SOULS / $25.99\nOne ticket to
  participate in the Epic Reads Meet Up with all four authors. Includes a
  copy of Kingdom of Souls and a signing line ticket. \nAbout the book: T
 he lush world building ofChildren of Blood and Bonemeets the sweeping sc
 ale ofStrange the Dreamerin this captivatingepicYA fantasy debut. \n4 BO
 OK BUNDLE DISCOUNT TICKET / $66.99\nGet 20% off when you buy all four ti
 tles as a bundle. One ticket to participate in the Epic Reads Meet Up wi
 th all four authors. Includes a copy of Five Dark Fates\, These Divided 
 Shores\, Serpent and Dove\, and Kingdom of Souls and a signing line tick
 et. \nWhat is the difference between the ticket options?\nThe only diffe
 rence between the ticket options listed above is the title included with
  the ticket. Get 20% off by purchasing all four titles in the 4 Book Bun
 dle Discount Ticket.\nWhat if the ticket option (book) I want is sold ou
 t? \nDue to popularity\, one option may sell out quickly. If there are o
 ther tickets available\, please select another title\, then email us thr
 ough Eventbrite and let us know your preferred title.\nWhat if the event
  sells out?\nIn order to keep the meet up experience intimate and person
 al\, Meet Up Tickets are limited. However\, if the Meet Up Tickets are s
 old out\, you will be able to purchase a Signing Line Only Ticket. The s
 igning line will begin after the Meet Up portion of the event. Signing L
 ine Only Tickets include admittance to the signing line and a copy of th
 e new book of your choice.\nHow can I buy additional copies of books?\nY
 ou only need one ticket to attend\, but you can buy the books by the oth
 er authors at the event. You can also order any of the authors titles fr
 om Quail Ridge Books ahead of time at here.\nWhere do I pick up my book/
 signing line ticket?\nYour book and your signing line ticket will be ava
 ilable at the event. You may pick up your book and ticket as early as 9:
 00 am on Tuesday\, September 3rd.\nWhen should I get there?\nSince you w
 ill have a reserved seat and signing line ticket you do not need to come
  hours early. However\, please allow some time for parking and book pick
 up. \nYou may pick up your book as early as 9:00 am on Tuesday\, Septemb
 er 3rd.\nWill the authors sign books at the event?\nYes\, following the 
 meet up\, all four authors will sign and personalize the title that came
  with your ticket. They will also sign any other titles. Purchase additi
 onal books here.\nPlease note that signing details are subject to change
 .\nHow are the reserved seats assigned?\nReserved seats and signing line
  tickets will be issued according to the date/time the ticket is purchas
 ed on Eventbrite. It does not matter which type of ticket you buy. Pleas
 e note\, tickets will sell quickly and it is to your advantage to purcha
 se early. If you would like to be seated in a group with friends\, you s
 hould buy your tickets together.\nHow is the signing line organized?\nTh
 e signing line ticket you will receive with your book will have a letter
  on it. When we call each letter\, you will line up to meet the authors.
  Letters are issued in the order in which your ticket was purchased\, so
  it is to your advantage to order early.\nNo one will be allowed in the 
 signing line without a signing line ticket.\nHow do I get there?\nFor GP
 S or mapping apps use:\nQuail Ridge Books\n4209-100 Lassiter Mill Road\n
 Raleigh NC 27609\nWhere can I park?\nThere is ample parking near JCPenne
 y within a short walk from the bookstore. For other options\, refer to t
 his map. North Hills provides a free shuttle service from anywhere in No
 rth Hills. For that service call 919-369-4089.\nWhat's the refund policy
 ?\nAttendees can receive refunds up to 7 days before the event date thro
 ugh Eventbrite. If you miss the refund window\, and are unable to make i
 t to the event\, you can pick up your signed book at Quail Ridge Books o
 n or after Saturday\, September 14th.\nDo I have to bring my printed tic
 ket to the event?\nYou can bring your printed ticket\, or you can show u
 s your ticket (with QR code) on your phone. You must show the ticket to 
 pick up your book and signing line ticket.
CREATED:20260313T024209Z
GEO:35.8385145;-78.6448158
LOCATION:Quail Ridge Books\, 4209-100 Lassiter Mill Road\, Raleigh\, NC 2
 7609
URL:https://www.eventbrite.com/e/epic-reads-ya-meet-up-at-quail-ridge-boo
 ks-tickets-65729979137
