SUMMARY:Veronica Roth at Quail Ridge Books - Paperback Tour
DESCRIPTION:https://www.eventbrite.com/e/veronica-roth-at-quail-ridge-boo
 ks-paperback-tour-tickets-57892550176\n\n#1 New York Times' Bestselling 
 Author Veronica Roth is coming to Quail Ridge Books! The author of the D
 ivergent and Carve the Mark series will be in conversation with author B
 rendan Reichs on Thursday\, April 4th at 7:00 pm. We anticipate this eve
 nt will sell out very quickly.\nEventbrite ticket sales have closed. We 
 may have some unreserved seating available on a first come\, first serve
 d basis. Please call Quail Ridge Books at 919-828-1588 for more info.\nF
 AQs\nDo I need to buy a book to attend the event? \nYes. We realize that
  you may have already read her books\, so there are six ticket options a
 nd each includes a different paperback title to give you flexibility to 
 choose your favorite. \nEach ticket gets you a reserved seat and a signi
 ng line ticket.\nDue to the popularity of this event\, we don't anticipa
 te having any free\, unreserved seats available.\nTicket Options:\n\n\nT
 HE FATES DIVIDE (CARVE THE MARK #2) PAPERBACK TICKET / $15.99\n\n\n One 
 ticket to see Veronica Roth at Quail Ridge Books. Includes a paperback c
 opy of The Fates Divide + tax\, a reserved seat\, and a signing line tic
 ket. \n\n\nCARVE THE MARK PAPERBACK TICKET / $15.99\n\n\nOne ticket to s
 ee Veronica Roth at Quail Ridge Books. Includes a paperback copy of Carv
 e the Mark+ tax\, a reserved seat\, and a signing line ticket. \n\n\nDIV
 ERGENT PAPERBACK TICKET / $15.99\n\n\nOne ticket to see Veronica Roth at
  Quail Ridge Books. Includes a paperback copy of Divergent+ tax\, a rese
 rved seat\, and a signing line ticket. \n\n\nINSURGENT PAPERBACK TICKET 
 / $15.99\n\n\nOne ticket to see Veronica Roth at Quail Ridge Books. Incl
 udes a paperback copy of Insurgent+ tax\, a reserved seat\, and a signin
 g line ticket. \n\n\nALLEGIANT PAPERBACK TICKET / $15.99\n\n\nOne ticket
  to see Veronica Roth at Quail Ridge Books. Includes a paperback copy of
  Allegiant+ tax\, a reserved seat\, and a signing line ticket. \n\n\nFOU
 R A DIVERGENT COLLECTION PAPERBACK TICKET / $15.99\n\n\nOne ticket to se
 e Veronica Roth at Quail Ridge Books. Includes a paperback copy of Four+
  tax\, a reserved seat\, and a signing line ticket. \nWhat is the differ
 ence between the ticket options? Why are there so many options?\nThe onl
 y difference between the ticket options listed above is the paperback ti
 tle included with the ticket. This is the paperback tour of The Fates Di
 vide.  However\, Veronica knows many of her fans will already have hardc
 over copies of The Fates Divide. She wanted her fans to have the choice 
 to have another paperback title signed.\nWhat if the ticket option (book
 ) I want is sold out? \nDue to popularity\, one option may sell out quic
 kly. If there are other tickets available\, please select another title\
 , then email us through Eventbrite and let us know your preferred title.
 \nHow can I buy additional copies of Veronica's books?\nYou can buy addi
 tional signed copies of Veronica's books at the event. \nHow can I buy c
 opies of Brendan Reichs' books?\nBrendan will also be signing his books 
 at the event. You can order his books from Quail Ridge Books ahead of ti
 me here. You may also purchase his books at the event. \nWhere do I pick
  up my book/ticket?\nYour book and your signing line ticket will be avai
 lable at the event. You may pick up your book and ticket as early as 9:0
 0 am on Thursday\, April 4th. \nDue to another event at Quail Ridge Book
 s that afternoon\, no seats will be available for the Veronica Roth even
 t until after 5:00 pm.\nWhen should I get there?\nSince you will have a 
 reserved seat and signing line ticket you do not need to come hours earl
 y. However\, please allow some time for parking and book pickup. \nYou m
 ay pick up your book as early as 9:00 am on Thursday\, April 4th.\nDue t
 o another event at Quail Ridge Books that afternoon\, no seats will be a
 vailable for the Veronica Roth event until after 5:00 pm.\nWill Veronica
  sign books at the event?\nDue to time constraints Veronica will only si
 gn and personalize ONE (1) book per person. \nWhat if I want her to sign
  a book I already own?\nYour ticket will come with one of Veronica Roth'
 s paperbacks. Veronica will only sign ONE (1) book in the signing line\;
  however\, that book does not need to be the book that came with your ti
 cket. \nCan I take photos?\nYou may take candid photos during the presen
 tation and while in the signing line. However\, because of the crowd siz
 e and time constraints\, there will be no posed photos. If you'd like to
  take a picture with Veronica while she is signing your book\, a QRB boo
 kseller will be on hand to take the photo with your camera or phone. \nH
 ow are the reserved seats assigned?\nReserved seats and signing line tic
 kets will be issued according to the date/time the ticket is purchased o
 n Eventbrite. It does not matter which type of ticket you buy. Please no
 te\, tickets will sell quickly and it is to your advantage to purchase e
 arly. \nYour reserved seat will be for any seat in an assigned row. The 
 row number will be listed on the ticket you pick up with your book. \nHo
 w is the signing line organized?\nThe signing line ticket you will recei
 ve with your book will have a letter on it. When we call each letter\, y
 ou will line up to meet Veronica. Letters are issued in the order in whi
 ch your ticket was purchased\, so it is to your advantage to order early
 .\nNo one will be allowed in the signing line without a signing line tic
 ket.\nHow do I get there?\nFor GPS or mapping apps use:\nQuail Ridge Boo
 ks\n4209-100 Lassiter Mill Road\nRaleigh NC 27609\nWhere can I park?\nTh
 ere is ample parking near JCPenney within a short walk from the bookstor
 e. For other options\, refer to this map. North Hills provides a free sh
 uttle service from anywhere in North Hills. For that service call 919-36
 9-4089. \nWhat's the refund policy?\nAttendees can receive refunds up to
  7 days before the event date through Eventbrite. If you miss the refund
  window\, and are unable to make it to the event\, you can pick up your 
 signed Veronica Roth paperback at Quail Ridge Books on or after Friday\,
  April 5th. \nDo I have to bring my printed ticket to the event?\nYou ca
 n bring your printed ticket\, or you can show us your ticket (with QR co
 de) on your phone. You must show the ticket to pick up your book and sig
 ning line ticket.\n\n\n
